# STT Providers: deepgram, elevenlabs, google
# LLM Providers: minimax, gemini, openai, anthropic
# TTS Providers: cartesia, elevenlabs, google, azure
# Avatar Providers: css, threejs, readyplayer
# Managed avatar room path: LiveKit + Simli / LiveAvatar
# Hosted note: keep OPENAI_API_KEY populated for prod/staging. The default session UI uses OpenAI Realtime even when the backend lesson path uses other LLM providers.
# Prefer FIREBASE_WEBAPP_CONFIG for local/prod parity. The public NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_* keys remain as a fallback.
# Firebase Auth note: local Google sign-in also needs your dev host in Firebase Console -> Authentication -> Settings -> Authorized domains.
# This repo defaults to http://127.0.0.1:3000, so add 127.0.0.1. Add localhost too if you use localhost:3000.
# LangSmith aliases accepted: LANGCHAIN_API_KEY, LANGCHAIN_PROJECT, LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2
